.DT
set_main_plural
Disk World creator help
set_main_plural

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_main_plural -  This method sets the main plural for the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_main_plural(mixed str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the main plural
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/desc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the main plural for the object.  The main plural
is like the short description for the pluralised object.  If this
is not set then the short will attempt to be pluralised to
figure it out.
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
set_main_plural("green wombles");

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
efun::pluralize(), query_plural(), query_main_plural(), set_short(), add_plural()
.EP

